    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/headerwireup.png?t=1731027768\" /></span><br>通过连接各种<strong>模块</strong>来创造角色的不同能力。一些模块生产能量、一些能存储或修改能量类型、剩下的则将能量转化为效果。<strong>搭建强大的结构</strong>来消灭敌人或在把能量存入电池以备不时之需。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/rack3.gif?t=1731027768\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/headerzap.png?t=1731027768\" /></span><br>每个回合将能量引导到哪都是一个<strong>战术问题</strong>：是导入爆能枪模块直接攻击敌人，还是导入减速枪来控制战场上的时间线？是使用治疗药水恢复生命，还是将能量存入电池准备下个回合打一发大的？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/battle.gif?t=1731027768\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/headerturnbased.png?t=1731027768\" /></span><br><br>在这个破碎的世界中，<strong>因果律</strong>都被破坏了。通过灵活操控引力荷<strong>在时间线上前后移动</strong>来：躲避火山喷发和雷击，从敌人面前溜过，甚至将敌人送入强力的的引力尖峰。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/timeline3.gif?t=1731027768\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/headerroguelike.png?t=1731027768\" /></span><br>你的冒险将穿越各种生物群落，各种难缠的敌群都有可能毁掉你。巧妙地连接机架上的各种模块，来应对<strong>随机生成的</strong>不断增加的威胁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/levels2.gif?t=1731027768\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317800/extras/landscape2.png?t=1731027768\" /></span>",
